---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Service Areas | Aurora, Lawrenceburg, Dearborn County | Probst Excavating"
  description="Probst Excavating proudly serves Aurora, Lawrenceburg, Dearborn County, and the entire Tri-State area (Indiana, Ohio, Kentucky) with professional excavation services."
>
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">
      Service Areas
    </h1>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <section class="mb-12">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-6">
          Probst Excavating Services is proud to serve Aurora, Lawrenceburg, and the entire 
          Tri-State area with professional excavation and site development services.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Primary Service Areas</h2>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-8">
          <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Aurora, Indiana</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Our home base and primary service area. We have extensive experience working 
              with Aurora's unique terrain and local regulations.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Lawrenceburg, Indiana</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Serving the Lawrenceburg community with reliable excavation services for 
              residential and commercial projects.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Dearborn County, IN</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              We serve all of Dearborn County with comprehensive excavation and site 
              development solutions.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Tri-State Area</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Our services extend throughout the Tri-State region, including parts of 
              Indiana, Ohio, and Kentucky.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Communities We Serve</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
            <li>Aurora, IN</li>
            <li>Lawrenceburg, IN</li>
            <li>Greendale, IN</li>
            <li>Bright, IN</li>
            <li>Hidden Valley, IN</li>
          </ul>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
            <li>Dillsboro, IN</li>
            <li>Moores Hill, IN</li>
            <li>Sunman, IN</li>
            <li>West Harrison, IN</li>
            <li>Manchester, IN</li>
          </ul>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
            <li>Rising Sun, IN</li>
            <li>Florence, KY</li>
            <li>Union, KY</li>
            <li>Harrison, OH</li>
            <li>And surrounding areas</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12 bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Local Expertise Matters</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          With over 20 years of experience working in Dearborn County and the surrounding 
          Tri-State area, we understand the unique challenges of our region:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-4">
          <li><strong>Soil Conditions:</strong> We know the local terrain and how to work with it effectively</li>
          <li><strong>Weather Patterns:</strong> Our experience helps us plan around seasonal challenges</li>
          <li><strong>Local Regulations:</strong> We're familiar with county and municipal requirements</li>
          <li><strong>Community Knowledge:</strong> We understand the specific needs of local homeowners and businesses</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Not Sure If We Serve Your Area?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          If you're located in southeastern Indiana, southwestern Ohio, or northern Kentucky 
          and need excavation services, we encourage you to reach out. We may be able to 
          accommodate projects outside our typical service area.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-blue-600 text-white p-6 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">Contact us to discuss your project!</h3>
          <p class="mb-4">
            We're happy to provide free estimates and consultations for projects throughout 
            the Tri-State area.
          </p>
          <a 
            href="/contact" 
            class="inline-block bg-white text-blue-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-gray-100 transition"
          >
            Get Your Free Estimate
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="bg-gray-900 text-white mt-16 py-8">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <p class="text-gray-400">
        Â© {new Date().getFullYear()} Probst Excavating Services. All rights reserved.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mt-2">
        Aurora, IN | Family-Owned & Operated Since 2004
      </p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</BaseLayout>
